metadata.name: STARRY NIGHT
metadata.description:
Character Design inspired by the painting “Starry Night” by Vincent van Gogh (1889)

A female soldier that pierces the night with passion brighter than the luminous sky.

Dimension: 3000px x 3500px
Artist: ChinChin
Created on: December 26th, 2021

Collector will receive the original file via email. 
With love,
ChinChin

P/s: Since it is the first NFT, all bidders will receive a stamp of this character <3
